<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA_Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>New Question Notification</title>

    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f6f9;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        p {
            color: #555555;
        }
        .container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #333333;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #999999;
            text-align: center;
        }
    </style>

</head>
<body>
    <h1>Hello <%= adminName %>,</h1>
    <p>We hope you're doing well! A new question has been posted in your course titled "<%= title %>." The question was asked by <%= name %> (<%= senderEmail %>).</p>

        <p>We encourage you to review and respond to the question to keep the discussion going.</p>
        <p>Thank you for your commitment to helping your students succeed! We truly appreciate your effort in providing great learning experiences.</p>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>Best Regards,</p>
            <p>Your <strong>Course Platform</strong> Team.</p>
        </div>
</body>
</html>